                <p class="lead">Google Analytics (<a href="https://www.google.com/analytics/learn/privacy.html" target="_blank">https://www.google.com/analytics/learn/privacy.html</a>)</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="lead">Firebase (<a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a>)</p>
              </li>
